{"tid":166661,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手睇睇台北7日行程","createTime":"2017-03-22T09:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T08:56:52.000Z","uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91415995fc9ac0dfe38a1022d46b66c59d219caf","tid":166661,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"第一次帶屋企人去旅行,幫手望望,<br />\n費事兩老搭車,應該會包車,<br />\n酒店已經book晒<br />\n<br />\n9/4 Day 1<br />\n傍晚時間到酒店(住大安區eclat),預計係下晝5點,之後去西門紅樓行下,食晚飯<br />\n<br />\n10/4 Day2<br />\n宜蘭一日遊,10點係酒店開車,會去宜蘭甲子蘭酒文物館,宜蘭設治紀念館,宜蘭文學館,金車威士忌酒廠,香草菲菲芳香植物博物館,晚餐係羅東夜市搞掂<br />\n<br />\n11/4 Day3<br />\n去烏來,小烏來天空步道,大溪老茶廠,大溪老街, 巧克力共和國<br />\n夜晚我同老婆睇Coldplay,兩老返台北酒店先<br />\n<br />\n12/4 Day4<br />\n早上食完早餐就check out, book左12點去食養山房, 之後去陽明山出霧溫泉旅館CHECK IN,再去金山老街行下,夜晚返酒店食飯,浸下溫泉<br />\n<br />\n13/4 Day5<br />\n係酒店食完早餐就check out,之後係陽明山行下,擎天崗大草原,冷水坑溫泉竹子湖海芋園,係嗰度食個晏,睇埋台北市花卉試驗中心,返台北市內酒店check in,食飯,可能去饒河街夜市<br />\n<br />\n14/4 Day6<br />\n淡水,士林一日遊,具體行程未諗<br />\n<br />\n15/4 Day 7<br />\n最後一日,係台北市內行下,松山文創園,國父記念館,四四南村,國立故宮博物院,夜晚係信義三越嗰邊食<br />\n<br />\n16/4 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以俾D意見,或者有咩食肆可以介紹下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad5092b8da2f166cb3eb368ecbed3ce195280dc","tid":166661,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"無老鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89d462e86df92220d07dc498879b083a522a7dd","tid":166661,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無老鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5049a7ff925f1342aa035a218ff7cea715de822e","tid":166661,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無老鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超好食嘅湯底<br />\n食完返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1ed58cd5a0bdc62d52c942e6a0f84c4a67d44a","tid":166661,"uid":69340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"馬辣"},{"pid":"e8dd019ff49034cc6bdbb7ce9318977fd6863ad9","tid":166661,"uid":4142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"鼎王 <br />\n無老鍋<br />\n<br />\n兩間都係打邊爐<br />\n都好好食 一定要試哂佢<br />\n高度推薦"},{"pid":"865854dc7c029a0b991a2919b168a9ca6fb089b0","tid":166661,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"明白，安排下先"},{"pid":"83b1a9ab033ea6fc7db4a9648fb2b4b0e4923569","tid":166661,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:11:18.000Z","msg":"宜蘭 唔係台北喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n國立故官博物館, 要行半日架, 如果你睇晒咁多館.<br />\n如果走馬看花1-2個鐘都得嘅."},{"pid":"7746ecbbd8e8acf0b6c74dd5db3fc2bcf1f09bca","tid":166661,"uid":73237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"宜蘭邊夠時間睇咁多地方呀....<br />\n<br />\n淡水可以去探草泥馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85873d163ec2c2ee81a80402914e25be1a2013c","tid":166661,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜蘭邊夠時間睇咁多地方呀....<br />\n<br />\n淡水可以去探草泥馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nKAVALAN我一定要去,其他其實無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2acffef19c649c8d8bfa2d3abc6ff7f776bb4a","tid":166661,"uid":7823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:48:14.000Z","msg":"帶下佢地去夜市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974b021a349828d038832e79876fe1b31a75fe73","tid":166661,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:58:40.000Z","msg":"將松山文創園區擺落day6啦 行完食埋嘢先入淡水<br />\nday7太多地方喇行撚死兩老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0d77b72231bc7c4254348be63ebae5675f80c9","tid":166661,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"想問西門紅樓嗰邊有咩好食?"},{"pid":"e1b63d5f2d12c8cadf8a40f7418f2844d69c08b9","tid":166661,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問西門紅樓嗰邊有咩好食?</blockquote><br />\n阿財虱目魚"},{"pid":"6c6dcb3a6b20ccc218d243f238f13a333b5fbeea","tid":166661,"uid":92412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"巴打你行咁多館唔悶架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如去下平溪線會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fffcf12aca39f6eaa6da7af5f39b7d5a8922f3","tid":166661,"uid":58169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次帶屋企人去旅行,幫手望望,<br />\n費事兩老搭車,應該會包車,<br />\n酒店已經book晒<br />\n<br />\n9/4 Day 1<br />\n傍晚時間到酒店(住大安區eclat),預計係下晝5點,之後去西門紅樓行下,食晚飯<br />\n<br />\n10/4 Day2<br />\n宜蘭一日遊,10點係酒店開車,會去宜蘭甲子蘭酒文物館,宜蘭設治紀念館,宜蘭文學館,金車威士忌酒廠,香草菲菲芳香植物博物館,晚餐係羅東夜市搞掂<br />\n<br />\n11/4 Day3<br />\n去烏來,小烏來天空步道,大溪老茶廠,大溪老街, 巧克力共和國<br />\n夜晚我同老婆睇Coldplay,兩老返台北酒店先<br />\n<br />\n12/4 Day4<br />\n早上食完早餐就check out, book左12點去食養山房, 之後去陽明山出霧溫泉旅館CHECK IN,再去金山老街行下,夜晚返酒店食飯,浸下溫泉<br />\n<br />\n13/4 Day5<br />\n係酒店食完早餐就check out,之後係陽明山行下,擎天崗大草原,冷水坑溫泉竹子湖海芋園,係嗰度食個晏,睇埋台北市花卉試驗中心,返台北市內酒店check in,食飯,可能去饒河街夜市<br />\n<br />\n14/4 Day6<br />\n淡水,士林一日遊,具體行程未諗<br />\n<br />\n15/4 Day 7<br />\n最後一日,係台北市內行下,松山文創園,國父記念館,四四南村,國立故宮博物院,夜晚係信義三越嗰邊食<br />\n<br />\n16/4 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以俾D意見,或者有咩食肆可以介紹下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅樓裝修緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 圍起哂<br />\n陽明山花鐘個邊有櫻花睇，我前幾日去個時擎天崗太大霧，乜都睇唔到，你上車前問下司機，唔係就要搭成日<br />\n陽明山建議book草山夜未眠，好正，六點去到可以睇成個台北入夜個境好靚"},{"pid":"73331d718b8e7fada4b188fa689a83d402efe8a3","tid":166661,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一次帶屋企人去旅行,幫手望望,<br />\n費事兩老搭車,應該會包車,<br />\n酒店已經book晒<br />\n<br />\n9/4 Day 1<br />\n傍晚時間到酒店(住大安區eclat),預計係下晝5點,之後去西門紅樓行下,食晚飯<br />\n<br />\n10/4 Day2<br />\n宜蘭一日遊,10點係酒店開車,會去宜蘭甲子蘭酒文物館,宜蘭設治紀念館,宜蘭文學館,金車威士忌酒廠,香草菲菲芳香植物博物館,晚餐係羅東夜市搞掂<br />\n<br />\n11/4 Day3<br />\n去烏來,小烏來天空步道,大溪老茶廠,大溪老街, 巧克力共和國<br />\n夜晚我同老婆睇Coldplay,兩老返台北酒店先<br />\n<br />\n12/4 Day4<br />\n早上食完早餐就check out, book左12點去食養山房, 之後去陽明山出霧溫泉旅館CHECK IN,再去金山老街行下,夜晚返酒店食飯,浸下溫泉<br />\n<br />\n13/4 Day5<br />\n係酒店食完早餐就check out,之後係陽明山行下,擎天崗大草原,冷水坑溫泉竹子湖海芋園,係嗰度食個晏,睇埋台北市花卉試驗中心,返台北市內酒店check in,食飯,可能去饒河街夜市<br />\n<br />\n14/4 Day6<br />\n淡水,士林一日遊,具體行程未諗<br />\n<br />\n15/4 Day 7<br />\n最後一日,係台北市內行下,松山文創園,國父記念館,四四南村,國立故宮博物院,夜晚係信義三越嗰邊食<br />\n<br />\n16/4 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以俾D意見,或者有咩食肆可以介紹下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅樓裝修緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 圍起哂<b